{"tid":497433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果以四億美元收購音樂辨識服務商 Shazam","createTime":"2017-12-12T17:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T15:15:39.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"95f251813545957d8faae7627d902d6285145a20","tid":497433,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T17:55:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/771263399732397/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F771263399732397%2F&d=ZUEwTQyDNCO0O%2BjS2JMtiAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d69cb33b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/771263399732397/</a><br />\n<br />\n消息指，蘋果只以 4 億美元收購約 10 億美元估值的 Shazam。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果指，Shazam 在世界各平台共有過億用戶，能夠藉幫助用家發掘新音樂，加強蘋果音樂串流服務。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果音樂目前用戶數量有 2,700 萬，遠低過對手 Spotify 的 6,000 萬。<br />\n<br />\nShazam 現時亦支援 Android 手機用戶，但蘋果也沒有透露，未來會否終止 Shazam 服務 Andriod 用戶。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#Shazam　#音樂辨識　#蘋果 #收購　#Andriod　#音樂串流服務"},{"pid":"6ecf1d065cebdd1ff46c8c3032d649c18b675d3b","tid":497433,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T18:13:04.000Z","msg":"時事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513aaef2a7c8670e4db8aa077b0ac337d079f8c6","tid":497433,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T18:16:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3852fee687af544947afeba3078825627582c2fb","tid":497433,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:47:49.000Z","msg":"Shazam!!!!!!"},{"pid":"e6d14e443813002625fbed0e8385680eb2adcf5c","tid":497433,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:52:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e5bab05b99fca2e98afa215853c01e774b427a7","tid":497433,"uid":83906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:08:10.000Z","msg":"租service 同買公司係咪真係咁難分？"},{"pid":"fd5a04019bd066f0bdf70